# Wide base → cross shaft → wide capital. Classic column profile in one cube height.

# --- BASE (sy=0, full 3x3) ---
S 0 0 0  0 0 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 0 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 0 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  0 0 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 0 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 0 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  0 0 2  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 0 2  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 0 2  Stone

# --- SHAFT (sy=1, cross — narrower than base) ---
S 0 0 0  1 1 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  0 1 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 1 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 1 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 1 2  Stone

# --- CAPITAL (sy=2, full 3x3) ---
S 0 0 0  0 2 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 2 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 2 0  Stone
S 0 0 0  0 2 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 2 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 2 1  Stone
S 0 0 0  0 2 2  Stone
S 0 0 0  1 2 2  Stone
S 0 0 0  2 2 2  Stone
